title: Tech women place second, men third at Big 12s - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech women place second, men third at Big 12s - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team closed out the Big 12 Outdoor Championships as the women placed second with 162 points and the men third with 118 points.
